.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22756%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Kosters'%20Justin%2C%20Texas%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68673facf748d8c055f4ff69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22567%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Kosters'%20Justin%2C%20Texas%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lance%20and%20Michelle%20Koster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20home%20in%20Justin%20is%203%2C500%20square%20feet%20and%20has%20five%20bedrooms%20and%20three%20bathrooms%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20space%20for%20my%20wife%2C%20me%2C%20and%20our%20two%20teenage%20sons.%20We%20live%20in%20a%20new%20neighborhood%20developed%20by%20homebuilder%20KB%20Homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20really%20like%20our%20neighborhood.%20It%20has%20both%20larger%20and%20smaller%20homes%2C%20which%20was%20perfect%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife's%20mother%20was%20living%20with%20us%20in%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20and%20when%20we%20moved%20to%20Texas%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20home%20with%20a%20mother-in-law%20suite%2C%20but%20we%20weren't%20having%20much%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20larger%20home%20that%20would%20fit%20the%20four%20of%20us%2C%20and%20a%20smaller%20home%20for%20my%20mother-in-law%2C%20also%20in%20the%20same%20neighborhood.%20She%20now%20lives%20about%20a%20quarter%20mile%20from%20us%20and%20is%20fully%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4a5b42e-6893-483d-bec4-42091cf878a2%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20pros%20and%20cons%20to%20living%20in%20Texas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Salt%20Lake%20Valley%2C%20where%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20sits%2C%20has%20a%20population%20of%20almost%202%20million%20people%2C%20so%20even%20though%20we%20lived%20in%20a%20suburban%20area%2C%20it%20still%20felt%20pretty%20busy.%20Life%20is%20a%20lot%20slower%20in%20Justin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20town%20has%20a%20little%20downtown%2C%20with%20a%20small%20grocery%20store%20a