r%20key%20AI%20insights%2C%20and%20let%20them%20act.%20The%20AI%20agents%20generate%20suggestions%2C%20and%20the%20human%20validates%20and%20approves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20piloting%20this%20now%20with%20some%20major%20clients%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20an%20incredible%20success.%20That's%20how%20we're%20thinking%20about%20the%20convergence%20of%20digital%20and%20human%20workforces%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20managing%20them%20together%2C%20but%20creating%20systems%20where%20AI%20augments%20people%20in%20a%20seamless%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe6fff88-ed93-434d-978f-8c301571363c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20provide%20an%20example%20of%20these%20applications%20in%20action%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20a%20cruise%20director%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%2C%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20things%20that%20impact%20how%20my%20guests%20enjoy%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20makeup%20of%20the%20people%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20the%20weather%2C%20what%20day%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you're%20on%20a%20day%20at%20sea%2C%20or%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20a%20port%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20that%20stuff.%20There's%20data%20to%20be%20found%20there%20on%20what%20happens%20and%20how%20the%20guests%20behave.%20I%20mean%20like%20their%20buying%20activities%2C%20where%20they%20like%20to%20hang%20out%2C%20those%20types%20of%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20can%20harness%20that%20information%20with%20AI%20agents%20to%20actually%20understand%20and%20predict%20what's%20going%20to%20happen.%20We%20know%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20tomorrow's%20weather%20is%20going%20to%20be%20bad%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20day%20at%20sea.%20We%20know%20historically%20how%20all%20of%20that%20affects%20the%20movement%20of%20people%20and%20the%20consumption%20of%20products%2C%20whether%20that%20be%20merchandise%2C%20food%2C%20or%20beverages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20recommend%20that%20you%20take%20half%20of%20the%20people%20from%20this%20venue%20and%20move%20them%20to%20this%20venue.%20We%20recommend%20moving%20around%20products%20so%20you%20don't%20run%20out%2C%20because%20we%20know%20what%20demand%20is%20going%20to%20look%20like.%20We%20recommend%20redeploying%20people%20to%20do%20different%20things%20in%20anticipation%20of%20this.%20The%20AI%20will%20turn%20around%20and%20list%20out%20and%20build%20out%20that%20process%20automatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20human%20in%20the%20loop%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20that%20makes%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20change%20this%20piece.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20through%20a%20very%20visual%2C%20nice%20interface.%20They%20click%20go%2C%20and%20then%20there's%20a%20chain%20of%20orchestration%20that%20happens%2C%20in%20which%20people%20are%20notified%2C%20leadership%20is%20notified%2C%20supply%20chain%20changes%20on%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275eb1f2c-a56f-4637-b31f-a0caca3885df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20value%20of%20up-skilling%20here%3F%20How%20much%20do%20employees%20need%20to%20learn%20about%20AI%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20just%20know%20that%20they%20have%20a%20screen%20and%20an%20application%20that%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BHere's%20how%20much%20stuff%20you%20have%20now%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHere's%20how%20many%20you%20have%20coming%20inbound%2C%26quot%3B%20maybe.%20They%20don't%20need%20to%20know%20how%20the%20technology%20works.%20This%20idea%20of%20up-skilling%20the%20entire%20workforce%20to%20use%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20it's%20kind%20of%20silly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22790c0c35-c86d-4cbd-9ef2-89dd7d4fcfd2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20are%20you%20helping%20companies%20think%20through%20questions%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20look%20at%20the%20functions%20%E2%80%94%20rethink%20that.%20That%20also%20dovetails%20into%20the%20people%20part%2C%20right%3F%20You're%20not%20only%20just%20giving%20them%20technology%20that's%20AI-enabled%2C%20you're%20allowing%20them%20to%20start%20to%20rethink%20how%20they%20do%20their%20job%2C%20and%20how%20they%20can%20be%20more%20efficient%20at%20the%20job%2C%20and%20also%20provide%20more%20overall%20value%20and%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-consulting-exec-jason-noel-ai-integration-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751647002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6860587485e81483682d0147%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-consulting-exec-jason-noel-ai-integration-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jason%20Noel%2C%20the%20new%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20EY's%20Americas%20Consulting%20arm%2C%20gets%20specific%20on%20AI%20in%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A58%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-consulting-exec-jason-noel-ai-integration-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Sinners%E2%80%99%20Producer%20Says%20Costumes%20Were%20Purchased%20From%20Marvel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Blade%E2%80%99%20Reboot%20That%20%E2%80%98Ended%20Up%20Not%20Shooting%E2%80%99%3A%20They%20Had%20a%20%E2%80%98Warehouse%20Full%20of%20Period-Appropriate%20Clothes%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751646940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMCDSINN_WB037_c5174c.jpg%3Fcrop%3D0px%252C71px%252C1280px%252C720px%26resize%3D1000%252C563%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236447479%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CSinners%E2%80%9D%20gave%20audiences%20a%20sneak%20peek%20at%20Marvel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CBlade%E2%80%9D%20reboot%20without%20them%20even%20knowing.%20During%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20ScreenCrush%2C%20%E2%80%9CSinners%E2