%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20exist%2C%20the%20staunchly%20anti-Trump%20news%20website%20The%20Bulwark%20might%20not%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20president%20isn't%20solely%20responsible%20for%20The%20Bulwark's%20success.%20Instead%2C%20its%20top%20editor%20credits%20email%20newsletters%2C%20podcasts%2C%20and%20YouTube%20for%20its%20impressive%20growth%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20grew%20consistently%2C%20all%20the%20way%20through%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Jonathan%20V.%20Last%2C%20editor%20of%20The%20Bulwark%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20something%20I%20didn't%20expect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Trump's%20resurgence%20has%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20that%20Last%20and%20his%20colleagues%20were%20kindling.%20The%20Bulwark%20surpassed%20100%2C000%20paid%20subscribers%20on%20Substack%20in%20early%20July%2C%20which%20the%20company%20told%20BI%20is%20more%20than%20double%20its%20total%20in%20late%20October%20%E2%80%94%20just%20before%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bulwark%20also%20now%20has%20830%2C000%20total%20subscribers%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20get%20its%20emails%20for%20free.%20The%20company%20said%20its%20total%20count%20has%20tripled%20in%20the%20last%20year%20and%20surpassed%20500%2C000%20a%20day%20after%20Trump%20retook%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20is%20another%20key%20part%20of%20The%20Bulwark's%20growth.%20It%20crossed%201%20million%20subscribers%20on%20the%20platform%20in%20mid-February%2C%20and%20that%20count%20rose%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E34%25%20between%20then%20and%20early%20July%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20healthy%20mix%20of%20short-form%20snippets%20and%20long-form%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20site%20uses%20YouTube%20Shorts%2C%20the%20platform's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebu