rom%20The%20Atlantic's.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Last%20said%20many%20Bulwark%20readers%20are%20largely%20on%20the%20center%20left%20to%20the%20center%20right%2C%20he%20added%20that%20the%20main%20common%20thread%20among%20his%20reader%20base%20is%20a%20distaste%20for%20authoritarianism.%20To%20Last%2C%20that's%20synonymous%20with%20an%20unease%2C%20or%20outright%20disgust%2C%20with%20Trump%20and%20many%20of%20his%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20on%20a%20team%2C%20and%20the%20team%20is%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Last%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Last%20said%20The%20Bulwark%20doesn't%20have%20a%20vendetta%20against%20Trump.%20If%20the%20president%20enacts%20policies%20that%20Last%20and%20his%20colleagues%20like%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foperation-warp-speed-us-coronavirus-vaccine-program-pfizer-moderna-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOperation%20Warp%20Speed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20accelerated%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20development%20during%20the%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20he%20said%20they'll%20gladly%20tout%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20reflexively%20negative%2C%26quot%3B%20Last%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20if%20Trump%20comes%20out%20and%20says%20that%20'ice%20cream%20is%20good%2C'%20we%20have%20to%20say%2C%20'ice%20cream%20is%20bad.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Last's%20readers%20know%20that%20he%20sees%20Trump%20as%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20American%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20described%20the%20events%20of%202020%20to%20somebody%20in%202016%2C%20they%20would've%20said%2C%20'You're%20crazy%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20%26quot%3BTrump%20Derangement%20Syndrome%2C%26quot%3B'%26quot%3B%20Last%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20may%20shrug%20off%20The%20Bulwark's%20warnings%20as%20alarmist%2C%20but%20Last%20insists%20he's%20not%20crying%20wolf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20people%20aren't%20fre