D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68309ae5ca50259add4ce9b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221311%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20exhausting%20to%20witness%20as%20a%20parent%20who%20just%20wanted%20them%20to%20enjoy%20themselves%2C%20this%20rivalry%20created%20an%20unexpected%20advantage%20in%20Australian%20football.%20When%20other%20children%20their%20age%20feared%20being%20tackled%20and%20hesitated%20to%20go%20for%20the%20ball%2C%20Charlie%20and%20Thomas%20showed%20remarkable%20courage%2C%20diving%20for%20possession%20with%20ferocity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20talent%20didn't%20go%20unnoticed.%20At%20a%20friend's%20birthday%20party%2C%20while%20the%20kids%20played%20casual%20football%20in%20the%20yard%2C%20a%20local%20junior%20coach%20spotted%20their%20skills%20and%20their%20aggressive%20tackling%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20no%20fear%20of%20being%20tackled%2C%20likely%20because%20they'd%20been%20tackling%20each%20other%20ruthlessly%20for%20years.%20The%20coach%20told%20me%20that%20most%20kids%20take%20years%20to%20develop%20that%20fearlessness.%20He%20recruited%20them%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20and%20they%20joined%20his%20team%20the%20very%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2c0e8f7-49a2-4220-a7fa-d21a2ae84425%5C%22%3EIntense%20competition%20sent%20us%20to%20the%20emergency%20room%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-morgans-competitive-drive-makes-her-uswnt-icon-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echanneling%20their%20competitiveness%20positively%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20encouraging%20them%20to%20view%20themselves%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btwin%20force%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20field%2C%20passing%20to%20each%20other%20and%20using%20their%20connection%20as%20an%20advantage.%20I%20half-jokingly%20hoped%20they'd%20develop%20some%20form%20of%20twin%20telepathy%20to%20dominate%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20their%20rivalry%20occasionally%20went%20too%20far.%20After%20watching%20the%20Australian%20football%20grand%20final%20on%20television%20(our%20equivalent%20of%20the%20Super%20Bowl)%2C%20they%20rushed%20into%20the%20backyard%20to%20play%20a%20game.%20Fueled%20by%20adrenaline%20and%20their%20unrelenting%20rivalry%2C%20they%20sprinted%20straight%20at%20each%20other%2C%20like%20a%20game%20of%20chicken.%20Neither%20backed%20down%2C%20and%20the%20resulting%20collision%20left%20both%20boys%20with%20gashed%20foreheads%20and%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20emergency%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Child%20at%20hospital%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68309b466ffb6822ec615ba0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20of%20the%20author's%20twins%20got%20injured%20playing.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20incident%20particularly%20tested%20my%20patience.%20Both%20qualified%20for%20an%20athletics%20tournament%20%E2%80%94%20Thomas%20in%20the%20long%20jump%20and%20Charlie%20in%20the%20100%20meters.%20Charlie%20checked%20the%20schedule%20and%20told%20me%20the%20event%20times%20so%20I%20could%20drive%20them%20the%20next%20day.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20arrived%2C%20we%20discovered%20the%20long%20jump%20competition%20had%20already%20concluded.%20Thomas%20was%20devastated.%20Charlie%20just%20shrugged%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20should've%20checked%20the%20times%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228440f7be-7b4c-46d0-b210-f194c8a0693c%5C%22%3EAcademic%20competition%20brought%20new%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20entered%20their%20final%20years%20of%20high%20school%2C%20their%20rivalry%20shifted%20to%20academics.%20They%20focused%20more%20on%20outscoring%20each%20other%20than%20on%20their%20actual%20grades.%20Even%20if%20one%20failed%20an%20assignment%2C%20he'd%20still%20celebrate%20if%20he%20outperformed%20his%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dynamic%20became%20particularly%20challenging%20during%20their%20final%20year.%20Thomas%20took%20a%20studious%20approach%2C%20selecting%20difficult%20subjects%20and%20dedicating%20countless%20hours%20to%20studying.%20He%20skipped%20parties%20and%20social%20events%20to%20prepare%20for%20exams.%20Charlie%20chose%20easier%20subjects%20and%20maintained%20a%20more%20laid-back%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Australia%2C%20college%20admission%20depends%20entirely%20on%20final%20exam%20results%3B%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20application%20process.%20When%20the%20results%20were%20released%2C%20we%20were%20on%20a%20flight%20to%20Chicago.%20They%20opened%20their%20phones%20simultaneously%20to%20check%20their%20scores%2C%20then%20looked%20at%20each%20other%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20other%20to%20speak%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20putting%20in%20half%20the%20effort%2C%20Charlie%20scored%20higher%20than%20his%20academically%20driven%20brother.%20Charlie's%20look%20of%20satisfaction%20contrasted%20sharply%20with%20Thomas's%20neutral%20expression.%20As%20a%20parent%2C%20I%20found%20it%20challenging%20to%20celebrate%20Charlie's%20achievement%20while%20watching%20Thomas%2C%20slightly%20disappointed%2C%20despite%20getting%20a%20high%20grade.%20He'd%20done%20everything%20%26quot%3Bright%26quot%3B%20and%20still%20come%20in%20second%2C%20at%20least%20in%20that%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8efda18-b1ba-4617-a5a0-b8ab8e321632%5C%22%3EThey%20also%20protect%20each%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParenting%20competitive%20twins%20has%20meant%20managing%20intense%20rivalry%20that%20can%20be%20heartbreaking%20at%20times.%20While%20most%20siblings%20compete%2C%20few%20are%20judged%20side%20by%20side%20so%20directly%20in%20sports%2C%20academics%2C%20and%20nearly%20every%20milestone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20them%20to%20strive%20for%20excellence%2C%20but%20not%20at%20each%20other's%20