amgail%20returned%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20he%20had%20been%20working%20as%20a%20wildlife%20biologist%2C%20to%20take%20over%20as%20director.%20His%20mission%20was%20to%20continue%20the%20work%20of%20building%20harmony%20between%20people%20and%20predators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20conservancy%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20initiatives%20is%20a%20livestock%20insurance%20scheme%20designed%20to%20reduce%20human-wildlife%20conflict%2C%20a%20common%20issue%20in%20pastoral%20communities.%20Each%20household%20contributes%20Rs%20400%20per%20year%20to%20a%20village%20fund.%20If%20a%20snow%20leopard%20kills%20livestock%2C%20the%20family%20is%20compensated%2C%20they%20receive%20Rs%205%2C000%20for%20a%20small%20animal%20and%20Rs%207%2C000%20for%20a%20larger%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20alongside%20the%20ferocious%20predator%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20dream%20for%20the%20pastoral%20communities%20of%20Ladakh.%20But%20maintaining%20their%20livelihoods%20through%20schemes%20like%20this%20makes%20it%20possible.%20Namgail%20says%20the%20felines%20are%20fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98Ri%20Gyancha%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98ornaments%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETourism%20that%20gives%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20in%20attitude%20is%20partly%20due%20to%20the%20economic%20incentives%20linked%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20snow%20leopards.%20A%20major%20success%20story%20has%20been%20the%20Himalayan%20Homestay%20Programme%2C%20launched%20in%202001.%20It%20began%20with%20a%20simple%20idea%2C%20instead%20of%20building%20tourist%20camps%20that%20generate%20waste%2C%20why%20not%20have%20visitors%20stay%20in%20local%20homes%3F%20The%20conservancy%20surveyed%20villages%20and%20found%20strong%20support%20for%20the%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%2