%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20ecological%20balance%20has%20knock-on%20effects.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20days%20we%20are%20receiving%20more%20rain%20and%20less%20snow.%20As%20the%20rainwater%20flows%20down%20the%20slopes%2C%20the%20loose%20soil%20also%20goes%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20soil%20is%20loosened%20by%20the%20grazing%20activity%20of%20goats.%20The%20presence%20of%20the%20snow%20leopard%20can%20help%20reduce%20such%20erosion%2C%20offering%20some%20protection%20against%20the%20increasing%20risk%20of%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThreats%20on%20the%20horizon%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20are%20growing%20threats.%20Ladakh%20is%20home%20to%20a%20natural%20community%20of%20carnivores%2C%20including%20wolves%2C%20lynx%2C%20brown%20bears%2C%20foxes%2C%20and%20now%20feral%20dogs.%20But%20unlike%20the%20others%2C%20feral%20dogs%20are%20a%20man-made%20crisis.%20They%20pose%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20both%20snow%20leopards%20and%20wolves%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20will%20only%20worsen%20if%20left%20unchecked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfrastructure%20development%20also%20risks%20fragmenting%20important%20corridors%20that%20connect%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20snow%20leopards%20to%20populations%20across%20Tibet%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20Karakoram.%20Its%20distinct%20ecological%20and%20cultural%20identity%20calls%20for%20context-specific%20development.%20One-size-fits-all%20models%20from%20elsewhere%20are%20unlikely%20to%20work%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20model%20for%20the%20Himalayas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouragingly%2C%20the%20survey%20aligns%20with%20international%20frameworks%20like%20PAWS%20(Population%20Assessment%20of%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Snow%20Leopards)%2C%20offering%20a%20model%20that%20can%20be%20replicated%20across%20the%20Himalayas.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20about%20tracking%20snow%20leopards%2C%20the%20same%20data%20and%20m