roblem.%20Developed%20by%20Dr%20Rajul%20Patkar%2C%20co-founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318062%2Fiit-bombay-scientist-dr-rajul-patkar-innovates-portable-soil-testing-device-for-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProximal%20Soilsens%20Technologies%2C%20%E2%80%98NutriSens%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20being%20called%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20smallest%20soil%20testing%20system.%20This%20handheld%20device%20offers%20accurate%20and%20lab-like%20results%2C%20not%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20but%20in%20under%20five%20minutes.%20And%20all%20it%20takes%20is%20a%20few%20simple%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20how%20you%20can%20use%20NutriSens%20to%20test%20your%20soil%20quickly%20and%20easily%2C%20without%20any%20lab%20visits%2C%20delays%2C%20or%20guesswork%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NutriSens%20offers%20accurate%20and%20lab-like%20results%2C%20not%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20but%20in%20under%20five%20minutes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-B