20station%2C%20helping%20them%20draft%20legal%20complaints%2C%20or%20simply%20being%20a%20patient%20listener%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20step%20in%20as%20trusted%20intermediaries.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20limited%20to%20Bengaluru%20%E2%80%94%20he%E2%80%99s%20helped%20people%20across%20Mumbai%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20even%20rural%20areas%20with%20limited%20digital%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20work%20spans%20sensitive%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20child%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20financial%20scams%2C%20stalking%2C%20caste-based%20harassment%2C%20gendered%20violence%20and%20sometimes%2C%20the%20threats%20come%20directly%20to%20him.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20death%20threats%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20physically%20assaulted%20by%20police%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20But%20he%20refuses%20to%20back%20down.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20not%20me%2C%20then%20who%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20just%20crisis%20response%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20Broseph%E2%80%99s%20work%20apart%20is%20the%20long-term%20nature%20of%20support.%20He%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20rescuing%20someone%20from%20an%20abusive%20situation.%20If%20someone%20needs%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F451896%2Fqueer-mental-health-therapy-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etherapy%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20arranges%20it.%20If%20someone%20has%20a%20court%20hearing%20but%20no%20one%20to%20accompany%20them%2C%20he%20sends%20a%20volunteer.%20If%20someone%20has%20nowhere%20to%20go%2C%20their%20network%20helps%20them%20find%20safe%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img_11zon-1751457272.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22htt