%E2%80%99s%20decided%20not%20to%20look%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20country%20where%20systemic%20support%20is%20hard%20to%20come%20by%2C%20and%20survivors%20are%20often%20gaslit%20or%20silenced%2C%20Broseph%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20stands%20as%20proof%20that%20change%20is%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20one%20rescued%20life%2C%20one%20answered%20call%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751459400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img_11zon-1751457272.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D460251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20people%20across%20India%20turn%20to%20him%20when%20the%20internet%20turns%20dangerous.%20Who%20is%20this%20silent%20digital%20saviour%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F460251%2Fbengalurus-batman-cybercrime-st-broseph-dushyant-dubey%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nine%20deaths%20in%20Europe%20linked%20to%20'silent%20killer'%20heatwave%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751447880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-berlin-cathedral-heatwave_6955511.jpg%3F20250702153700%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsilent-killer-heatwave-thought-to-have-left-at-least-9-dead-in-europe-13391343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20nine%20people%20in%20Europe%20have%20died%20in%20savage%20heat%20this%20week%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsilent%20killer%26quot%3B%20heatwave%20continues%20to%20bake%20the%20continent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsilent-killer-heatwave-thought-to-have-left-at-least-9-dead-in-europe-13391343%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22U.S.%20Retail